title: Recluse & Debonaire Cigars
itunes:title: Recluse & Debonaire Cigars
description: We look back at the best cigars of 2012 in preparation for this year's acclaimed Cigar of the Year! We're smoking two brand new cigars: the Iconic Recluse Kanu #2, and the Debonaire Ultra Premium.
